    "Algorithm 4The pseudo-code for SIAUI.Input: user perturbed interaction sequence S 𝑢 𝑖, user uploaded parameters M 𝑟 +1 𝑢 𝑖, the global model M 𝑟, LLM-based item embedding table V 𝑙𝑙𝑚 Output: inferred user 𝑢 𝑖 sequence S 𝑢 𝑖 1: S 𝑢 𝑖 = ∅ 2: V 𝑡𝑟𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑒𝑑 𝑢 𝑖 ← select trained items according to the changes of item embeddings in M 𝑟 +1 𝑢 𝑖 and M 𝑟 3: for 𝑣 𝑡 ∈ S 𝑢 𝑖 do 4: 𝑣 𝑢 𝑖 𝑡 ← replace 𝑣 𝑡 using E.q.",
